
# Online shopping application

We would like to build a shopping application which is used to order products and keep knowledge of quantity of products and send notifications using spring boot application.

## API Reference

### Create

```http
  POST /api/V1.0/product
```

`Request Body`:
```yaml
{
     "name" : "product1",
     "description" : "This is description of product1",
     "price" : 100,
     "category" : "OTHERS"
}
```

`Response`:
```yaml
NA1

```

### Read ALL

```http
  GET /api/V1.0/product
```

`Response`:
```yaml
NA1

```

### Read

```http
  GET /api/V1.0/product?name={productName}&category={productCategory}
```

`Response`:
```yaml
NA1

```

### Update

```http
  PUT /api/V1.0/product
```

`Request Body`:
```yaml
{
     "name" : "product1",
     "description" : "This is description of product1",
     "price" : 100,
     "category" : "OTHERS"
}
```

`Response`:
```yaml
{
    "subscriptionID": 2,
    "userID": 2,
    "startDate": "2023-02-15",
    "endDate": "2023-08-15"
}

```

### Delete

```http
  GET /api/v1.0/product?name={productName}

```

`Response`:
```yaml
NA1

```

